title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 28 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 28 2022
description:
DeSantis gives live update on Hurricane Ian. Joe Bastardi, Chief Forecaster at WeatherBell Analytics LLC and the author of The Weaponization of Weather in the Phony Climate War, joins C&B to give us an update on slow-moving Hurricane Ian -- and how our country's screwed up supply chain will impact the recovery, as well as the fascinating history of Hurricanes in Florida. C&B: Don't be afraid of being called transphobic. Christine Drazen takes lead in Oregon governor's race after interview with C&B.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
